title: Dolphins' Grimes says he's not distracted by wife's arrest
text: > Florida Dolphins' Grimes says he's not distracted by wife's arrest CORRECTS TO ARRESTED BEFORE, NOT AFTER THE GAME - This photo made available by the Miami-Dade Department of Corrections, shows Miko Grimes, wife of Miami Dolphins player Brent Grimes under arrest, Sunday, Sept. 27, 2015. Grimes faces charges of disorderly conduct, battery on a police officer and resisting arrest with violence. Grimes was arrested before the Miami Dolphins game against the Buffalo Bills. (Miami-Dade Department of Corrections via AP)
